verbose_text: 62 Interestingly, PCDH17 expression tends to show upregulation during this stage of neuronal differentiation in both BPD patients (BPD iPSCs versus BPD neurons, P-value < 0.001) and control cell systems (control iPSCs versus control neurons, P-value < 0.001) (XREF_FIG), suggesting this gene may be involved in early brain development.
